data.title: Ruthenian Voivodeship, L'vivs'ka city council Podcast
data.meta_description: If you want to explore a little-known piece of European history, let yourself be transported to the Ruthenian Voivodeship. This region, active from 1434 to 1772, was a fascinating mix of Eastern and Western Slavic cultures, with its pulsating heart in the city of Lviv. Imagine for a moment the hi...
